1
00:01:30,220 --> 00:01:32,980
Episode 22

2
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:35,710
You need to seize the opportunity.

3
00:01:35,950 --> 00:01:36,510
Her niece

4
00:01:36,510 --> 00:01:37,590
just had an accident.

5
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:39,310
Her dad is sick and came for treatment.

6
00:01:39,510 --> 00:01:40,510
It's just an excuse.

7
00:01:40,760 --> 00:01:42,070
Getting money is the real goal.

8
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:43,200
At this time...

9
00:01:43,350 --> 00:01:44,840
That's not seizing the opportunity.

10
00:01:45,070 --> 00:01:46,760
It's taking advantage of her misfortune.

11
00:01:48,590 --> 00:01:49,560
It's kinda the same.

12
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:51,350
You know your mom is very anxious.

13
00:01:51,510 --> 00:01:52,200
Besides,

14
00:01:52,310 --> 00:01:53,430
Fang Wanzhi is really great.

15
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:55,070
She's worthy of you,

16
00:01:55,150 --> 00:01:55,790
Ziwei!

17
00:01:59,710 --> 00:02:00,310
Good morning.

18
00:02:01,710 --> 00:02:02,760
Good morning, Mr. Yan.

19
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,200
No matter how busy

20
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,790
you are with work,

21
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:08,000
you still work out.

22
00:02:08,430 --> 00:02:09,150
That's really nice.

23
00:02:10,310 --> 00:02:11,030
It's my first

24
00:02:11,190 --> 00:02:12,240
exercise this week.

25
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:13,360
If you'd like,

26
00:02:13,710 --> 00:02:15,430
would you like to run
with me every morning?

27
00:02:17,430 --> 00:02:18,430
7 AM.

28
00:02:18,590 --> 00:02:19,150
It's settled.

29
00:02:26,470 --> 00:02:27,080
Have some water.

30
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,150
Thank you.

31
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,240
You ran too fast.

32
00:02:30,590 --> 00:02:31,280
I'd like

33
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:33,520
to invite someone to dinner tonight.

34
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,520
Could you

35
00:02:36,470 --> 00:02:37,470
find me a nice,

36
00:02:37,870 --> 00:02:38,560
elegant place

37
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:39,630
suitable for

38
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:40,360
conversation?

39
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,280
Of course.

40
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,710
Is this person

41
00:02:42,710 --> 00:02:43,360
an elder?

42
00:02:43,430 --> 00:02:43,960
About my age.

43
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,120
A man or a woman?

44
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,190
A woman.

45
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:48,310
She's very important to me.

46
00:02:50,310 --> 00:02:51,750
Do you like Western

47
00:02:51,910 --> 00:02:52,800
or Chinese food?

48
00:02:53,190 --> 00:02:53,910
What do you think?

49
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:57,520
Why don't you ask her opinion?

50
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,630
Western food then.

51
00:03:00,910 --> 00:03:01,750
It's the weekend.

52
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,240
Could you arrive first...

53
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:03,910
Of course.

54
00:03:03,910 --> 00:03:05,280
I'll prepare for the reception.

55
00:03:05,630 --> 00:03:06,430
I'll bring

56
00:03:06,710 --> 00:03:07,360
my own drinks.

57
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,520
President Yan, let me.

58
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:27,560
It's okay.

59
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:28,430
I'll get it.

60
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,800
How do you like the environment?

61
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:36,630
This restaurant

62
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,150
isn't in our

63
00:03:38,190 --> 00:03:39,240
company directory, is it?

64
00:03:39,750 --> 00:03:40,310
No.

65
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:41,710
This is a place I found after

66
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:42,430
joining Hongtu.

67
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,310
Just in case.

68
00:03:51,310 --> 00:03:52,280
You really are the best

69
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,710
colleague I've had

70
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:55,680
since coming here.

71
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:57,280
And you look really

72
00:03:57,710 --> 00:03:58,520
beautiful today.

73
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:01,870
Please sit.

74
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:03,630
My guest today

75
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,710
is you, Ms. Fang.

76
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:07,960
Mr. Yan, please don't joke.

77
00:04:08,310 --> 00:04:09,240
I'm not joking.

78
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:10,590
It's true.

79
00:04:10,870 --> 00:04:11,910
I brought this.

80
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:17,510
It has the same birth year as you.

81
00:04:17,950 --> 00:04:18,750
I went to great

82
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:20,310
lengths to find it.

83
00:04:21,270 --> 00:04:22,830
I have to go now.

84
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:27,680
Ms. Fang.

85
00:04:30,070 --> 00:04:31,390
Ms. Fang.

86
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:32,600
Ms. Fang.

87
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,560
I wanted to surprise you.

88
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:36,270
But I didn't know

89
00:04:36,430 --> 00:04:37,360
it would upset you.

90
00:04:37,750 --> 00:04:38,430
If it's work,

91
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:39,920
I don't have the right.

92
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:40,630
You do.

93
00:04:40,950 --> 00:04:41,920
This isn't work.

94
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:43,430
Actually,

95
00:04:43,870 --> 00:04:45,360
I just wanted to have

96
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:46,950
a simple date with you.

97
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:48,120
Date?

98
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:49,680
Is this simple?

99
00:04:50,870 --> 00:04:51,680
I'm sorry.

100
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:54,240
I misspoke again.

101
00:04:57,160 --> 00:04:57,870
You...

102
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:00,310
What are you laughing at?

103
00:05:00,950 --> 00:05:02,160
I'm sorry, Mr. Yan.

104
00:05:03,390 --> 00:05:04,240
It seems you really

105
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:05,630
have no dating experience.

106
00:05:05,950 --> 00:05:07,070
And I disliked the whole

107
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:08,240
"bringing a bottle of wine

108
00:05:08,310 --> 00:05:09,680
with the same year as the

109
00:05:09,750 --> 00:05:10,750
girl's birth" thing.

110
00:05:13,070 --> 00:05:14,360
Sorry.

111
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,070
Mr. Yan!

112
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:22,600
How about I treat you to dinner?

113
00:05:23,510 --> 00:05:24,950
I know a good place.

114
00:05:38,870 --> 00:05:39,680
Please enjoy.

115
00:05:39,830 --> 00:05:40,480
Thank you.

116
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:45,510
Mr. Yan, you don't drink beer?

117
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,040
No.

118
00:05:48,190 --> 00:05:50,510
I actually really like beer.

119
00:05:51,950 --> 00:05:52,630
And this place

120
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,920
has a really lively atmosphere.

121
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:58,720
Actually, I've

122
00:05:58,750 --> 00:05:59,630
never been here before.

123
00:05:59,950 --> 00:06:01,360
It's close to your house.

124
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:02,720
I thought if you wanted

125
00:06:02,750 --> 00:06:04,000
to try something different,

126
00:06:04,270 --> 00:06:05,120
you could give it a try.

127
00:06:06,750 --> 00:06:08,950
You're really thoughtful.

128
00:06:09,630 --> 00:06:10,310
To be honest,

129
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:11,830
I've learned a lot

130
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,680
from you since I joined Hongtu.

131
00:06:14,430 --> 00:06:15,070
Thank you.

132
00:06:15,830 --> 00:06:16,600
Cheers.

133
00:06:16,950 --> 00:06:17,510
Come on.

134
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:23,040
Thank you for this beautiful evening.

135
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:25,750
I hope we can spend

136
00:06:26,510 --> 00:06:27,480
every weekend together

137
00:06:27,830 --> 00:06:29,160
from now on.

138
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,240
I mean,

139
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,390
have dinner together.

140
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:36,510
Tomorrow is Sunday.

141
00:06:37,430 --> 00:06:39,000
I have to go back to Hong Kong.

142
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:41,160
Can we continue tonight?

143
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:44,070
I really enjoy

144
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:45,390
chatting with you.

145
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:48,120
If you don't want to eat out,

146
00:06:48,430 --> 00:06:49,600
you can come to my place.

147
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,480
I can cook for you.

148
00:06:55,310 --> 00:06:56,390
I'll pass.

149
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:00,390
Okay.

150
00:07:01,070 --> 00:07:02,920
You probably have a lot of things to do.

151
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:05,600
Let's meet again next week.

152
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:06,270
Is that okay?

153
00:07:07,510 --> 00:07:08,680
I mean,

154
00:07:09,390 --> 00:07:10,920
would you like to try my cooking

155
00:07:11,430 --> 00:07:12,920
and some of my hometown dishes?

156
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:15,190
Sure. No problem.

157
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:26,000
Want to come

158
00:07:27,070 --> 00:07:28,270
up for another drink?

159
00:07:28,870 --> 00:07:29,430
No, thank you.

160
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,270
I'm not a big drinker.

161
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,680
It's okay if you don't drink.

162
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:34,040
We can hang out.

163
00:07:34,430 --> 00:07:36,040
We're meeting tomorrow, aren't we?

164
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,270
Yeah, right.

165
00:07:37,870 --> 00:07:40,040
I'll take you home.

166
00:07:41,070 --> 00:07:42,310
You don't need to.

167
00:07:42,510 --> 00:07:43,160
Alright.

168
00:07:49,070 --> 00:07:49,750
See you tomorrow!

169
00:08:16,390 --> 00:08:17,480
Goodnight, Mr. Yan.

170
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:19,000
Goodnight, Ms. Fang.

171
00:08:28,430 --> 00:08:29,830
Why are you so late?

172
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,000
Have you eaten?

173
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,080
Yes.

174
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:33,720
Your cooking

175
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,390
is really delicious.

176
00:08:35,510 --> 00:08:36,670
I ate it all.

177
00:08:38,790 --> 00:08:39,480
Did you smoke?

178
00:08:40,870 --> 00:08:41,480
No.

179
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:42,750
Really?

180
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:43,720
Yes.

181
00:08:45,150 --> 00:08:46,000
I believe you.

182
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,360
I want to ask you something.

183
00:08:49,390 --> 00:08:51,200
Can I go see Zhao Jun?

184
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,200
Of course.

185
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:01,030
This place is nice.

186
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,510
It's huge.

187
00:09:02,910 --> 00:09:03,910
I never even noticed

188
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:05,320
there was a staircase there.

189
00:09:09,750 --> 00:09:11,120
This place is lively.

190
00:09:11,510 --> 00:09:12,200
It has everything.

191
00:09:13,630 --> 00:09:14,320
Juan!

192
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:15,480
You're back?

193
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:15,840
Jun.

194
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:16,440
Mr. He!

195
00:09:17,790 --> 00:09:18,720
How's Guangzhou?

196
00:09:18,870 --> 00:09:19,750
Great.

197
00:09:19,750 --> 00:09:21,030
Orders placed.

198
00:09:21,150 --> 00:09:22,150
Goods shipped.

199
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:23,600
Payment received.

200
00:09:23,790 --> 00:09:24,600
Fantastic.

201
00:09:24,750 --> 00:09:25,910
Not me.

202
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,200
Zhao Jun is the amazing one.

203
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,240
She is

204
00:09:28,270 --> 00:09:29,550
incredibly smart.

205
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:31,440
The restaurant owner quit.

206
00:09:31,630 --> 00:09:33,390
She wants to rent it as a supermarket.

207
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:34,390
This is the best

208
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,440
location in Buji Town.

209
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:36,870
The rent is a bit expensive,

210
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:38,200
but the location is perfect.

211
00:09:38,390 --> 00:09:39,200
Juan,

212
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:40,840
I need a favor.

213
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,790
Can I move in and live with my

214
00:09:42,910 --> 00:09:43,510
granddaughter?

215
00:09:44,150 --> 00:09:45,480
Wanzhi's house

216
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:46,720
is too fancy.

217
00:09:46,870 --> 00:09:47,510
I always feel

218
00:09:47,670 --> 00:09:49,270
like a guest there.

219
00:09:49,550 --> 00:09:50,630
I can't sleep.

220
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:51,750
Please,

221
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:53,360
just take pity on me.

222
00:09:53,550 --> 00:09:55,030
I thought you came to see Zhao Jun.

223
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,510
I didn't expect you

224
00:09:56,510 --> 00:09:57,480
wanted to move.

225
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:58,960
Don't think you can smoke

226
00:09:58,960 --> 00:09:59,910
if you live here.

227
00:10:00,030 --> 00:10:00,910
No.

228
00:10:01,030 --> 00:10:01,790
Grandpa.

229
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:03,360
I'm much better now.

230
00:10:03,550 --> 00:10:04,910
If you write a guarantee promising

231
00:10:05,030 --> 00:10:05,960
not to smoke anymore,

232
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,440
I'll buy you a ticket

233
00:10:07,750 --> 00:10:08,720
back to Shenxian Peak.

234
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:09,440
No.

235
00:10:09,790 --> 00:10:10,840
It's so much better here.

236
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:11,910
There are big hospitals.

237
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,630
I just went to get an X-ray.

238
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:14,390
The doctor

239
00:10:14,550 --> 00:10:15,790
said I'm fine.

240
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:17,720
The doctor at Shenxian Peak
said I would die.

241
00:10:17,870 --> 00:10:18,750
I won't go back.

242
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:20,270
Grandpa,

243
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,840
you're so clinging to Aunt Wanzhi.

244
00:10:22,150 --> 00:10:22,870
What?

245
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:23,960
Uh...

246
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:26,600
Well,

247
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,630
she insisted on taking me to the doctor.

248
00:10:34,510 --> 00:10:35,960
Why don't you have dinner with us?

249
00:10:36,390 --> 00:10:37,510
Help me check out Yan Ziwei.

250
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:40,080
You want me to vet him?

251
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,240
Don't regret it.

252
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:44,120
No one treats you

253
00:10:44,790 --> 00:10:46,270
as well as Gao Xiang.

254
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:49,630
I already said

255
00:10:49,750 --> 00:10:51,550
Gao Xiang is just a friend.

256
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:53,720
Then I won't be a third wheel.

257
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:55,150
I'll take your dad

258
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:57,320
out to dinner tonight.

259
00:11:07,390 --> 00:11:07,910
Alright.

260
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,080
I'm done here.

261
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:10,440
You'll have to handle

262
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:11,600
the "love dinner" yourself.

263
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:14,080
What "love dinner"?

264
00:11:18,750 --> 00:11:19,360
My dad.

265
00:11:19,870 --> 00:11:20,750
Mr. He?

266
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,030
Not him.

267
00:11:22,390 --> 00:11:23,270
Mr. Meng?

268
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:26,790
Dad,

269
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:28,120
why are you

270
00:11:28,150 --> 00:11:29,320
calling me?

271
00:11:31,750 --> 00:11:32,440
In Shenzhen?

272
00:11:33,390 --> 00:11:34,150
Tonight?

273
00:11:35,030 --> 00:11:36,240
From 5 to 8.

274
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:40,480
I'll call

275
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:41,870
you back later to see

276
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:43,120
if you're coming over

277
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,000
or if I'm coming to you.

278
00:11:46,360 --> 00:11:47,320
My dad's in Shenzhen.

279
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:48,750
He wants to have dinner with me.

280
00:11:49,030 --> 00:11:49,670
Then I'll

281
00:11:50,270 --> 00:11:51,790
have to cancel my date with Yan Ziwei.

282
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:54,150
It's not good

283
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:55,360
to stand him up

284
00:11:55,790 --> 00:11:56,840
on your first date.

285
00:11:57,120 --> 00:11:57,960
What should I do?

286
00:11:59,270 --> 00:12:00,320
Mr. Meng is just in time.

287
00:12:00,670 --> 00:12:01,550
He can vet him for you.

288
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:02,600
One is

289
00:12:02,790 --> 00:12:03,670
a mayor.

290
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:04,720
The other's a CEO.

291
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:05,720
They will

292
00:12:05,790 --> 00:12:07,030
definitely have common ground.

293
00:12:07,630 --> 00:12:09,080
Is this a good idea?

294
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:10,550
What's wrong with it?

295
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:12,150
Don't you want

296
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:13,150
to date Yan Ziwei?

297
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:15,080
If things go well,

298
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:16,750
they'll have to meet sooner or later.

299
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:17,790
It's an essential

300
00:12:17,790 --> 00:12:19,320
part of dating.

301
00:12:20,910 --> 00:12:22,320
Isn't this too fast?

302
00:12:22,510 --> 00:12:23,790
This is just in time.

303
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:24,630
Mr. Meng doesn't

304
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:25,960
come to Shenzhen often.

305
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:27,720
That's true.

306
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:30,150
Alright, then.

307
00:12:36,630 --> 00:12:37,510
Okay.

308
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:39,150
Dad!

309
00:12:39,510 --> 00:12:40,000
Wanzhi!

310
00:12:41,150 --> 00:12:41,870
How have you been?

311
00:12:41,870 --> 00:12:42,670
I'm fine.

312
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:44,510
I brought you

313
00:12:44,750 --> 00:12:46,240
some local specialties.

314
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:47,390
Mr. Meng,

315
00:12:47,550 --> 00:12:48,320
let me.

316
00:12:48,390 --> 00:12:49,030
No need.

317
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:50,720
We can carry them.

318
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:51,670
Give them to me.

319
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:52,240
Okay.

320
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:52,870
- Be careful.
- Okay.

321
00:12:52,910 --> 00:12:53,840
I'm off then.

322
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:55,000
Come on.

323
00:12:57,030 --> 00:12:58,510
This apartment is nice.

324
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:00,120
The benefits

325
00:13:00,150 --> 00:13:01,320
are truly enviable.

326
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:03,030
Dad,

327
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:05,200
is your work at the CPPCC easy?

328
00:13:05,630 --> 00:13:06,360
You look much more

329
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,440
energetic than last time.

330
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:08,270
Really?

331
00:13:09,550 --> 00:13:10,720
But I'm

332
00:13:11,750 --> 00:13:13,270
no longer at the CPPCC.

333
00:13:13,790 --> 00:13:14,720
Where did you go?

334
00:13:15,030 --> 00:13:15,720
Jianglin City.

335
00:13:15,910 --> 00:13:16,720
Executive Vice Mayor.

336
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:18,390
Every city has a very

337
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:19,390
heavy task of attracting

338
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:20,240
investment now.

339
00:13:21,150 --> 00:13:22,000
So I'll be coming

340
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:23,150
here often in the future.

341
00:13:23,750 --> 00:13:24,630
You got promoted.

342
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:26,150
No, at the same level.

343
00:13:26,510 --> 00:13:27,960
You're given important responsibilities.

344
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:29,320
That's impressive.

345
00:13:30,320 --> 00:13:31,550
My girl is even more impressive.

346
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:34,320
You prepared so much food.

347
00:13:35,150 --> 00:13:36,720
Shenzhen has abundant supplies.

348
00:13:37,670 --> 00:13:39,240
It wasn't just prepared.

349
00:13:39,670 --> 00:13:40,910
I was planning to cook

350
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:41,840
at home today.

351
00:13:42,030 --> 00:13:43,030
So much food

352
00:13:43,080 --> 00:13:44,320
for you alone?

353
00:13:44,510 --> 00:13:45,910
You must be treating someone, right?

354
00:13:47,510 --> 00:13:48,320
Is it Gao Xiang?

355
00:13:48,630 --> 00:13:49,840
I called him.

356
00:13:49,870 --> 00:13:50,600
No.

357
00:13:50,720 --> 00:13:51,270
Did I

358
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:53,870
disrupt your plans?

359
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:55,030
No.

360
00:13:57,240 --> 00:13:58,270
I was planning to treat

361
00:13:58,440 --> 00:13:59,840
a friend to dinner today.

362
00:14:00,750 --> 00:14:02,320
He's the president of our company.

363
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:05,440
We just started seeing each other.

364
00:14:08,240 --> 00:14:09,630
I've come at a really bad time.

365
00:14:09,840 --> 00:14:10,960
No.

366
00:14:11,240 --> 00:14:12,480
You've come at the perfect time.

367
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:13,790
You can check him out.

368
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:15,550
Me? Check him out?

369
00:14:16,550 --> 00:14:17,510
I'm not qualified.

370
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:19,870
I enjoy chatting

371
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:21,360
with capable

372
00:14:21,670 --> 00:14:22,480
young people,

373
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,000
especially in Shenzhen.

374
00:14:24,440 --> 00:14:25,670
I learn a lot

375
00:14:25,720 --> 00:14:27,270
from talking to them.

376
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:28,200
It's really good.

377
00:14:38,870 --> 00:14:40,390
Sorry I'm late.

378
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:43,360
There were so many cars.

379
00:14:43,550 --> 00:14:44,200
There was traffic.

380
00:14:45,320 --> 00:14:45,870
It's okay.

381
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:47,720
I'm the one who should apologize.

382
00:14:48,150 --> 00:14:49,840
There will be one more person tonight.

383
00:14:50,320 --> 00:14:51,080
My dad's here.

384
00:14:51,840 --> 00:14:52,960
I hope you don't mind.

385
00:14:53,750 --> 00:14:54,550
I don't.

386
00:14:55,270 --> 00:14:56,150
I've thought of it.

387
00:14:56,790 --> 00:14:59,000
I picked out a gift for your dad.

388
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:01,200
What's this?

389
00:15:02,150 --> 00:15:02,910
A cigar.

390
00:15:03,510 --> 00:15:04,440
A lot of people

391
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:05,630
like this flavor.

392
00:15:06,120 --> 00:15:07,600
I chose it especially for him.

393
00:15:08,510 --> 00:15:09,670
My dad doesn't smoke.

394
00:15:11,670 --> 00:15:12,270
Really?

395
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:13,240
Yes.

396
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:14,480
Maybe you don't

397
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:16,480
know him well.

398
00:15:17,790 --> 00:15:18,670
Don't worry.

399
00:15:18,870 --> 00:15:20,480
I'll get along well with him.

400
00:15:21,030 --> 00:15:21,870
I'm confident.

401
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:27,720
But could you

402
00:15:28,630 --> 00:15:30,120
come over to my place

403
00:15:30,630 --> 00:15:32,440
for a while after dinner?

404
00:15:33,270 --> 00:15:34,240
Even if we only

405
00:15:34,790 --> 00:15:35,840
have one glass

406
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:37,840
of that wine each.

407
00:15:38,960 --> 00:15:40,750
It's okay if you don't want to drink.

408
00:15:41,910 --> 00:15:42,790
I just want

409
00:15:43,320 --> 00:15:44,910
a little time alone

410
00:15:45,630 --> 00:15:46,510
with you.

411
00:15:48,030 --> 00:15:48,960
Is that alright?

412
00:15:52,630 --> 00:15:53,390
Come on.

413
00:15:58,150 --> 00:15:59,670
How should I address you?

414
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:01,360
Mr. Yan?

415
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:04,320
Whatever you like.

416
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:06,550
Just call him by his name.

417
00:16:06,720 --> 00:16:07,720
His name is Yan Ziwei.

418
00:16:08,440 --> 00:16:09,270
This is my dad.

419
00:16:13,790 --> 00:16:14,440
Mr. Fang.

420
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:17,510
My dad's surname is Meng.

421
00:16:19,600 --> 00:16:20,480
Mr. Meng.

422
00:16:20,750 --> 00:16:22,550
Mr. Meng, where do you work?

423
00:16:23,480 --> 00:16:25,030
I work for the Jianglin government.

424
00:16:25,600 --> 00:16:26,510
This is my business card.

425
00:16:27,390 --> 00:16:28,030
Thanks.

426
00:16:28,840 --> 00:16:30,150
Executive Vice Mayor.

427
00:16:30,550 --> 00:16:31,440
Mayor?

428
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:36,270
Fang Wanzhi,

429
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:38,080
your dad is the mayor?

430
00:16:39,480 --> 00:16:40,870
He just arrived in Shenzhen today.

431
00:16:41,030 --> 00:16:41,790
My dad said

432
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:43,390
he likes chatting with young people.

433
00:16:43,720 --> 00:16:44,670
So you two talk.

434
00:16:44,840 --> 00:16:45,550
I'll go cook.

435
00:16:45,870 --> 00:16:47,080
You're in luck today.

436
00:16:47,390 --> 00:16:48,150
My dad brought

437
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:49,360
a lot of local specialties.

438
00:16:49,550 --> 00:16:50,840
Come on, Ziwei. Please sit.

439
00:16:52,150 --> 00:16:52,720
I'm just

440
00:16:52,750 --> 00:16:53,840
a civil servant.

441
00:16:55,440 --> 00:16:56,550
Wanzhi told me

442
00:16:57,320 --> 00:16:58,480
that your Hongtu Trading

443
00:16:58,790 --> 00:16:59,670
is quite large

444
00:17:00,440 --> 00:17:01,150
and diversified,

445
00:17:01,440 --> 00:17:02,360
focusing on the development

446
00:17:02,360 --> 00:17:03,390
of high-tech new products.

447
00:17:04,160 --> 00:17:05,270
I'm quite interested.

448
00:17:06,070 --> 00:17:06,830
I have many questions

449
00:17:06,880 --> 00:17:08,240
I'd like to ask you.

450
00:17:21,350 --> 00:17:21,960
Where is he?

451
00:17:23,640 --> 00:17:24,510
He took a phone call

452
00:17:24,790 --> 00:17:25,440
and went out.

453
00:17:31,440 --> 00:17:32,200
Where did he go?

454
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:33,830
I'm about to start cooking.

455
00:17:34,680 --> 00:17:35,750
He has responsibilities.

456
00:17:36,720 --> 00:17:37,680
He must have encountered

457
00:17:37,750 --> 00:17:38,680
some emergency.

458
00:17:39,030 --> 00:17:39,880
I handle all his

459
00:17:39,920 --> 00:17:41,270
emergencies for him,

460
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:42,720
unless it's at the company level.

461
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:44,030
That's possible.

462
00:17:45,160 --> 00:17:45,880
No rush.

463
00:17:46,720 --> 00:17:47,310
We can wait.

464
00:17:51,880 --> 00:17:52,720
Mrs. Yan,

465
00:17:53,110 --> 00:17:54,110
I need to see you.

466
00:17:55,880 --> 00:17:56,830
About what I said today,

467
00:17:57,440 --> 00:17:58,110
I regret it.

468
00:17:58,880 --> 00:17:59,830
What do you mean "no"?

469
00:18:00,160 --> 00:18:01,200
I'm a human too.

470
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:04,680
Mommy,

471
00:18:05,480 --> 00:18:06,480
I need to see Grandpa.

472
00:18:06,790 --> 00:18:07,480
Don't come with me.

473
00:18:07,880 --> 00:18:08,750
I'll go see him myself.

474
00:18:19,400 --> 00:18:20,070
(Hello,)

475
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:22,310
(the subscriber you
dialed is unavailable.)

476
00:18:22,400 --> 00:18:23,270
Unavailable?

477
00:18:23,830 --> 00:18:24,790
What the hell?

478
00:18:27,750 --> 00:18:28,270
Dad,

479
00:18:28,640 --> 00:18:29,310
I'll go cook.

480
00:18:29,590 --> 00:18:30,240
Let's eat first.

481
00:18:30,830 --> 00:18:31,480
Is that okay?

482
00:18:32,030 --> 00:18:33,590
After all, you invited Ziwei first.

483
00:18:34,550 --> 00:18:35,400
Let's wait a bit.

484
00:18:35,790 --> 00:18:36,720
Then I'll go find him.

485
00:18:50,200 --> 00:18:50,750
Coming!

486
00:18:54,920 --> 00:18:55,790
Who are you?

487
00:18:56,110 --> 00:18:57,640
Is Yan Ziwei home?

488
00:18:58,160 --> 00:18:58,790
Mr. Yan?

489
00:18:59,200 --> 00:19:00,790
He just went out.

490
00:19:01,310 --> 00:19:02,240
Where did he go?

491
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:04,270
Hong Kong, I think.

492
00:19:04,550 --> 00:19:05,790
I don't know the specifics.

493
00:19:08,590 --> 00:19:10,310
Have you always worked here?

494
00:19:10,830 --> 00:19:11,480
Not really.

495
00:19:11,720 --> 00:19:12,510
But I worked here

496
00:19:12,550 --> 00:19:13,440
for many years.

497
00:19:13,480 --> 00:19:14,400
I'm retired now.

498
00:19:14,750 --> 00:19:15,640
Today Mr. Yan

499
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:17,110
specifically called me to come back,

500
00:19:17,350 --> 00:19:18,550
saying he had a guest tonight.

501
00:19:18,790 --> 00:19:20,110
He asked me to make

502
00:19:20,350 --> 00:19:21,310
the house cozy.

503
00:19:21,510 --> 00:19:22,200
But

504
00:19:22,350 --> 00:19:23,030
after I finished,

505
00:19:23,310 --> 00:19:24,110
he left.

506
00:19:26,480 --> 00:19:27,720
But could you come over

507
00:19:28,480 --> 00:19:30,110
to my place for a while after dinner?

508
00:19:30,310 --> 00:19:31,830
It's okay if you don't want to drink.

509
00:19:32,200 --> 00:19:33,030
I just want

510
00:19:33,440 --> 00:19:35,110
a little time alone

511
00:19:35,830 --> 00:19:36,640
with you.

512
00:19:50,590 --> 00:19:51,110
Dad,

513
00:19:51,310 --> 00:19:52,480
why are you cooking?

514
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:54,270
Cooking with my girl

515
00:19:54,590 --> 00:19:55,510
is so much fun!

516
00:19:57,550 --> 00:19:58,400
Yan Ziwei asked me

517
00:19:58,750 --> 00:20:00,000
to apologize to you.

518
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:01,550
He has some work to do.

519
00:20:01,790 --> 00:20:02,480
I understand.

520
00:20:03,030 --> 00:20:04,510
My cured pork is absolutely amazing.

521
00:20:04,830 --> 00:20:05,790
I learned from Grandma Yu.

522
00:20:06,000 --> 00:20:06,550
Try it.

523
00:20:07,160 --> 00:20:08,350
Is it the taste you remember?

524
00:20:11,480 --> 00:20:12,070
How is it?

525
00:20:12,070 --> 00:20:13,200
Not bad, Dad.

526
00:20:13,750 --> 00:20:14,640
Okay. You can rest now.

527
00:20:14,720 --> 00:20:15,750
I'll finish the other dishes.

528
00:20:18,240 --> 00:20:19,000
Ziwei?

529
00:20:19,640 --> 00:20:20,240
Open the door.

530
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:27,240
Help me.

531
00:20:29,960 --> 00:20:30,400
Sorry

532
00:20:30,640 --> 00:20:31,240
I'm late.

533
00:20:31,440 --> 00:20:32,240
Gao Xiang?

534
00:20:33,030 --> 00:20:33,880
What are you doing?

535
00:20:34,750 --> 00:20:35,400
Fang Wanzhi,

536
00:20:35,480 --> 00:20:36,640
do you consider me a friend?

537
00:20:36,920 --> 00:20:37,790
It was Mr. Meng

538
00:20:37,830 --> 00:20:39,350
who notified me of your move.

539
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:41,030
What is this?

540
00:20:42,350 --> 00:20:43,240
You're heartless.

541
00:20:43,750 --> 00:20:44,790
But I can't be.

542
00:20:44,960 --> 00:20:45,590
Right?

543
00:20:46,310 --> 00:20:47,070
Look.

544
00:20:48,070 --> 00:20:49,270
The best CD player.

545
00:20:49,720 --> 00:20:50,880
The best speakers.

546
00:20:51,030 --> 00:20:52,110
And a tube amplifier.

547
00:20:52,440 --> 00:20:53,510
All made in Shenzhen.

548
00:20:53,510 --> 00:20:54,510
I've got you a complete set.

549
00:20:54,750 --> 00:20:55,480
I'll have it

550
00:20:55,550 --> 00:20:56,830
installed within two hours.

551
00:20:57,350 --> 00:20:58,270
No need.

552
00:20:58,510 --> 00:20:59,510
You can listen to music

553
00:20:59,510 --> 00:21:00,440
when you're feeling down.

554
00:21:00,510 --> 00:21:01,400
You'll need it.

555
00:21:01,960 --> 00:21:03,270
Two hours won't do.

556
00:21:03,440 --> 00:21:04,240
Mr. Meng.

557
00:21:04,510 --> 00:21:05,640
Are you cooking?

558
00:21:05,720 --> 00:21:06,720
I'm a pretty good cook.

559
00:21:07,510 --> 00:21:08,000
Gao,

560
00:21:08,160 --> 00:21:09,160
here's the thing.

561
00:21:09,310 --> 00:21:10,510
I have things to do in a bit.

562
00:21:10,830 --> 00:21:11,960
I have to leave before eight.

563
00:21:12,200 --> 00:21:13,200
After I leave,

564
00:21:13,310 --> 00:21:14,200
you two can set up

565
00:21:14,200 --> 00:21:15,240
the stereo at home.

566
00:21:15,550 --> 00:21:16,030
Okay?

567
00:21:16,110 --> 00:21:16,830
Okay.

568
00:21:18,640 --> 00:21:20,070
I invited him over.

569
00:21:23,270 --> 00:21:23,920
You're a busy man.

570
00:21:23,920 --> 00:21:25,000
How can I let you cook?

571
00:21:25,000 --> 00:21:25,920
Here, let me do it.

572
00:21:25,960 --> 00:21:26,510
It's alright.

573
00:21:26,790 --> 00:21:28,310
Go talk with Wanzhi.

574
00:21:28,480 --> 00:21:29,000
Can you cook?

575
00:21:29,000 --> 00:21:29,590
Just relax.

576
00:21:29,720 --> 00:21:30,480
Okay.

577
00:21:31,550 --> 00:21:32,240
Be careful.

578
00:21:32,400 --> 00:21:32,960
Don't worry.

579
00:21:37,310 --> 00:21:38,160
Sorry.

580
00:21:38,350 --> 00:21:38,920
I messed up

581
00:21:38,920 --> 00:21:40,350
your plans after all.

582
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:41,960
No.

583
00:21:43,400 --> 00:21:45,510
I'll explain to Yan Ziwei

584
00:21:45,750 --> 00:21:46,550
when he gets back.

585
00:21:46,920 --> 00:21:47,480
No need.

586
00:21:48,110 --> 00:21:49,240
He probably won't come.

587
00:21:50,830 --> 00:21:51,310
At least

588
00:21:51,400 --> 00:21:52,480
he came to keep you company.

589
00:21:53,070 --> 00:21:54,590
He even gave me a speaker set.

590
00:21:56,000 --> 00:21:57,720
Why did you give me speakers?

591
00:22:00,070 --> 00:22:01,550
Aren't you tone-deaf?

592
00:22:01,680 --> 00:22:02,590
You can practice at home.

593
00:22:03,030 --> 00:22:03,720
Go cook.

594
00:22:03,880 --> 00:22:04,960
She's always been tone-deaf.

595
00:22:05,110 --> 00:22:05,790
Dad!

596
00:22:06,510 --> 00:22:07,830
I already told Mr. Meng about our

597
00:22:07,880 --> 00:22:08,960
experience at the food stall.

598
00:22:09,310 --> 00:22:10,720
Do I need you to tell him?

599
00:22:10,830 --> 00:22:12,350
My dad knows. He's my dad.

600
00:22:12,350 --> 00:22:13,350
Of course he knows.

601
00:22:13,550 --> 00:22:14,550
I'm cooking. Be careful.

602
00:22:14,550 --> 00:22:15,400
Don't move.

603
00:22:15,400 --> 00:22:16,440
Can you cook? Hurry.

604
