I'm fine.

902
00:34:55,510 --> 00:34:57,150
Wait. I have something to ask you.

903
00:34:59,030 --> 00:34:59,630
What is it?

904
00:35:00,000 --> 00:35:00,960
I have a question for you.

905
00:35:02,070 --> 00:35:02,760
Fang Wanzhi

906
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:04,630
is so great.

907
00:35:05,920 --> 00:35:06,800
Why haven't you

908
00:35:06,840 --> 00:35:08,360
pursued her all these years?

909
00:35:08,840 --> 00:35:10,320
Don't tell me you don't like her.

910
00:35:10,360 --> 00:35:11,110
No one will believe it.

911
00:35:15,230 --> 00:35:17,150
You're right.

912
00:35:17,510 --> 00:35:19,360
I do like her.

913
00:35:19,590 --> 00:35:21,880
Then why don't you pursue her?

914
00:35:24,880 --> 00:35:26,110
Well,

915
00:35:26,230 --> 00:35:26,760
I...

916
00:35:26,840 --> 00:35:27,920
I can do anything,

917
00:35:28,190 --> 00:35:30,190
except pursue girls.

918
00:35:33,630 --> 00:35:34,880
When I was 18,

919
00:35:36,480 --> 00:35:37,510
I had what I thought

920
00:35:38,630 --> 00:35:40,840
was a passionate relationship.

921
00:35:41,440 --> 00:35:42,400
But what happened?

922
00:35:43,440 --> 00:35:45,320
She was just playing around,

923
00:35:46,320 --> 00:35:47,320
using me.

924
00:35:49,030 --> 00:35:50,320
After that, I got scared.

925
00:35:53,590 --> 00:35:54,800
Really scared.

926
00:35:59,840 --> 00:36:00,550
Juan.

927
00:36:01,360 --> 00:36:02,480
Here, have some water.

928
00:36:03,030 --> 00:36:03,840
No.

929
00:36:08,110 --> 00:36:08,880
Don't sleep here.

930
00:36:09,190 --> 00:36:10,070
Get inside.

931
00:36:10,280 --> 00:36:10,960
No...

932
00:36:11,320 --> 00:36:12,150
I won't go.

933
00:36:14,150 --> 00:36:14,920
Go.

934
00:36:15,590 --> 00:36:16,670
Fine.

935
00:36:22,070 --> 00:36:24,550
I've confronted

936
00:36:26,440 --> 00:36:27,710
Gao Xiang.

937
00:36:30,190 --> 00:36:32,400
It's not that he doesn't
want to pursue you.

938
00:36:34,000 --> 00:36:35,400
It's that he's afraid.

939
00:36:36,760 --> 00:36:38,230
Gao Xiang is

940
00:36:38,880 --> 00:36:40,510
quite similar to you.

941
00:36:41,190 --> 00:36:42,280
He also had

942
00:36:42,760 --> 00:36:45,960
a failed relationship before.

943
00:36:52,280 --> 00:36:53,190
Fang Wanzhi!

944
00:36:54,150 --> 00:36:55,280
Listen.

945
00:36:56,000 --> 00:36:58,190
You and Gao Xiang

946
00:36:58,280 --> 00:37:00,880
will definitely end up together.

947
00:37:01,710 --> 00:37:04,110
It's just a matter of time.

948
00:37:08,960 --> 00:37:10,070
The landlord regretted it?

949
00:37:10,480 --> 00:37:11,000
Yes.

950
00:37:11,230 --> 00:37:12,510
He said he finally got

951
00:37:13,190 --> 00:37:14,190
all the permits

952
00:37:14,230 --> 00:37:15,150
for the restaurant.

953
00:37:15,630 --> 00:37:16,840
Converting it to a supermarket

954
00:37:17,000 --> 00:37:17,760
would be a waste.

955
00:37:18,150 --> 00:37:19,070
He screwed

956
00:37:19,150 --> 00:37:20,230
over Zhao Jun.

957
00:37:21,480 --> 00:37:22,110
Have you paid

958
00:37:22,190 --> 00:37:23,190
the deposit for the shelves?

959
00:37:23,920 --> 00:37:24,760
Don't worry.

960
00:37:25,070 --> 00:37:26,030
Let's talk to him

961
00:37:26,360 --> 00:37:27,710
and try to get the deposit back.

962
00:37:27,960 --> 00:37:28,960
I'm not in a hurry.

963
00:37:29,510 --> 00:37:30,960
I've found a new place.

964
00:37:31,590 --> 00:37:32,230
Where?

965
00:37:32,840 --> 00:37:33,590
Downstairs.

966
00:37:34,320 --> 00:37:35,320
Downstairs?

967
00:37:36,550 --> 00:37:38,190
A supermarket downstairs?

968
00:37:38,630 --> 00:37:39,480
Yes.

969
00:37:39,800 --> 00:37:40,840
The rent will be at most

970
00:37:40,880 --> 00:37:42,070
a third of what it was before.

971
00:37:42,360 --> 00:37:43,280
That would make it easier.

972
00:37:43,710 --> 00:37:45,760
And I wouldn't need to rent a warehouse.

973
00:37:46,000 --> 00:37:46,590
It's close by.

974
00:37:46,920 --> 00:37:48,960
This room can be used for storage.

975
00:37:49,230 --> 00:37:50,440
I can save a lot of money.

976
00:37:51,070 --> 00:37:53,110
I called you two here

977
00:37:54,320 --> 00:37:55,670
because I thought you could talk

978
00:37:56,000 --> 00:37:57,320
to Pei about the rent.

979
00:37:57,760 --> 00:37:59,710
The lower the better, of course.

980
00:38:00,320 --> 00:38:02,230
It won't be easy.

981
00:38:02,550 --> 00:38:03,800
She only cares about money.

982
00:38:05,000 --> 00:38:06,110
She's a shrewd person.

983
00:38:06,800 --> 00:38:07,760
You should

984
00:38:07,880 --> 00:38:09,400
do business with people

985
00:38:09,760 --> 00:38:10,670
like that.

986
00:38:14,590 --> 00:38:16,670
Ms. Fang, this is our first
time playing mahjong.

987
00:38:17,030 --> 00:38:18,150
Do you know how to play?

988
00:38:19,070 --> 00:38:20,030
Let's try.

989
00:38:20,480 --> 00:38:22,440
You want to open a supermarket here?

990
00:38:22,630 --> 00:38:24,440
It's too noisy. No way.

991
00:38:24,760 --> 00:38:26,440
You play mahjong here every day.

992
00:38:26,630 --> 00:38:28,030
Don't you find it noisy?

993
00:38:28,150 --> 00:38:29,400
If I hadn't lost

994
00:38:29,510 --> 00:38:30,590
so badly before,

995
00:38:30,590 --> 00:38:32,230
I wouldn't play mahjong.

996
00:38:32,510 --> 00:38:34,840
This is just for entertainment.

997
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:36,630
This is

998
00:38:36,760 --> 00:38:38,000
definitely not going to win.

999
00:38:38,590 --> 00:38:39,230
Nine wan.

1000
00:38:40,360 --> 00:38:41,110
Three bamboo.

1001
00:38:42,920 --> 00:38:43,920
Three bamboo!

1002
00:38:44,070 --> 00:38:45,280
A sure win!

1003
00:38:45,670 --> 00:38:46,760
I need it.

1004
00:38:49,510 --> 00:38:50,550
I'm about to win.

1005
00:38:50,670 --> 00:38:51,320
Ms. Fang,

1006
00:38:51,400 --> 00:38:52,670
are you helping her on purpose?

1007
00:38:52,760 --> 00:38:53,550
Be careful.

1008
00:38:53,670 --> 00:38:54,920
Don't discard a winning tile.

1009
00:38:55,110 --> 00:38:56,190
Nobody will.

1010
00:38:56,360 --> 00:38:57,590
I'm in a dead hand.

1011
00:38:57,840 --> 00:38:58,550
Red Dragon.

1012
00:38:59,320 --> 00:39:01,030
Oh my god, Red Dragon!

1013
00:39:01,190 --> 00:39:02,030
I win!

1014
00:39:05,110 --> 00:39:06,590
I'm the dealer now.

1015
00:39:06,590 --> 00:39:07,840
Don't scold me.

1016
00:39:07,880 --> 00:39:09,550
Ms. Fang is smart.

1017
00:39:09,630 --> 00:39:10,190
Unlike us,

1018
00:39:10,510 --> 00:39:11,710
so stupid.

1019
00:39:12,840 --> 00:39:13,920
Is your niece

1020
00:39:14,030 --> 00:39:15,590
as smart as you?

1021
00:39:15,960 --> 00:39:18,230
Will she lose money in business?

1022
00:39:18,880 --> 00:39:19,920
My niece isn't

1023
00:39:20,230 --> 00:39:21,880
as smart as I am.

1024
00:39:22,760 --> 00:39:23,400
She's smarter

1025
00:39:23,710 --> 00:39:24,880
than me.

1026
00:39:26,190 --> 00:39:27,320
If you want to make profit,

1027
00:39:27,630 --> 00:39:28,880
I can talk to you about the rent.

1028
00:39:29,150 --> 00:39:30,630
But this place is too remote.

1029
00:39:30,760 --> 00:39:32,480
I don't think you'll ask for more.

1030
00:39:33,000 --> 00:39:34,190
If you want to make more,

1031
00:39:34,590 --> 00:39:36,840
I suggest you use the
rent as an investment.

1032
00:39:40,070 --> 00:39:41,030
Li Juan!

1033
00:39:41,280 --> 00:39:41,840
Come on.

1034
00:39:42,280 --> 00:39:43,960
Play a couple of rounds for me.

1035
00:39:44,150 --> 00:39:45,710
If you lose, it's on me.

1036
00:39:45,920 --> 00:39:46,960
Hey, Pei,

1037
00:39:46,960 --> 00:39:48,000
I don't know how.

1038
00:39:48,150 --> 00:39:49,440
You do. You definitely can.

1039
00:39:49,800 --> 00:39:50,480
Zhao Jun.

1040
00:39:52,000 --> 00:39:53,800
Let me treat you to tea.

1041
00:39:56,070 --> 00:39:57,230
Auntie Wanzhi can

1042
00:39:57,960 --> 00:39:58,840
handle anything.

1043
00:39:59,800 --> 00:40:00,550
She's amazing.

1044
00:40:01,070 --> 00:40:01,840
Except for herself,

1045
00:40:01,880 --> 00:40:02,880
though.

1046
00:40:03,510 --> 00:40:04,760
Are you still drunk?

1047
00:40:06,550 --> 00:40:07,400
There's another problem.

1048
00:40:09,030 --> 00:40:10,710
The name I came up with

1049
00:40:11,400 --> 00:40:12,630
doesn't suit the current location.

1050
00:40:13,320 --> 00:40:15,000
Why doesn't it suit?

1051
00:40:15,920 --> 00:40:17,480
The old location was bustling.

1052
00:40:17,960 --> 00:40:19,510
I wanted to call it Liangji Supermarket,

1053
00:40:20,190 --> 00:40:20,920
meaning the most

1054
00:40:21,070 --> 00:40:22,630
vibrant place in Buji Town.

1055
00:40:23,280 --> 00:40:24,550
But now there are fewer people.

1056
00:40:25,000 --> 00:40:25,760
We'd be laughed

1057
00:40:25,800 --> 00:40:26,760
at for that name.

1058
00:40:29,230 --> 00:40:29,920
Auntie Wanzhi,

1059
00:40:30,710 --> 00:40:31,920
help me come up with a name.

1060
00:40:32,360 --> 00:40:33,510
It needs to be

1061
00:40:33,760 --> 00:40:34,800
catchy and memorable.

1062
00:40:35,400 --> 00:40:36,480
She's not some

1063
00:40:36,590 --> 00:40:37,440
all-powerful fairy.

1064
00:40:37,800 --> 00:40:38,630
I trust Auntie Wanzhi.

1065
00:40:40,670 --> 00:40:42,800
This is really hard.

1066
00:40:43,000 --> 00:40:44,760
Naming a shop is an art.

1067
00:40:44,880 --> 00:40:46,030
Let's find a feng shui master.

1068
00:40:46,440 --> 00:40:47,590
Two hundred yuan

1069
00:40:47,630 --> 00:40:48,630
can get ten names.

1070
00:40:48,920 --> 00:40:50,110
You can choose any you like.

1071
00:40:50,230 --> 00:40:50,960
Two hundred?

1072
00:40:51,440 --> 00:40:52,150
That's too expensive.

1073
00:40:52,510 --> 00:40:53,320
Give me the money.

1074
00:40:53,480 --> 00:40:54,880
I'll give you 100 names.

1075
00:40:55,280 --> 00:40:56,030
Grandpa,

1076
00:40:56,230 --> 00:40:57,110
you're a money-grubber!

1077
00:40:57,400 --> 00:40:58,630
Money-grubber?

1078
00:40:58,880 --> 00:41:00,190
I'm the poorest old man

1079
00:41:00,280 --> 00:41:01,400
in Shenxian Peak.

1080
00:41:01,760 --> 00:41:03,440
I don't want you to waste your money.

1081
00:41:08,190 --> 00:41:08,920
Shenxian Peak?

1082
00:41:09,510 --> 00:41:10,480
That's a good name.

1083
00:41:10,710 --> 00:41:12,320
How about Shenxian Peak Supermarket?

1084
00:41:12,880 --> 00:41:13,710
No way.

1085
00:41:13,960 --> 00:41:15,110
Such a corny name

1086
00:41:15,150 --> 00:41:16,190
in Shenzhen would

1087
00:41:16,360 --> 00:41:17,880
bankrupt the business.

1088
00:41:18,150 --> 00:41:18,710
Mr. He,

1089
00:41:19,000 --> 00:41:19,670
not corny at all.

1090
00:41:20,190 --> 00:41:21,480
I think Shenxian Peak sounds

1091
00:41:21,510 --> 00:41:22,360
really nice.

1092
00:41:23,150 --> 00:41:24,590
It makes people want to go there.

1093
00:41:25,070 --> 00:41:25,760
Right?

1094
00:41:26,880 --> 00:41:27,630
Let me think about it.

1095
00:41:28,400 --> 00:41:29,710
If you think this is okay,

1096
00:41:31,030 --> 00:41:32,110
then I'll go with it.

1097
00:41:34,590 --> 00:41:35,360
That's settled then.

1098
00:41:35,760 --> 00:41:36,840
Remember to eat.

1099
00:41:38,230 --> 00:41:39,360
I'll call you again on Sunday.

1100
00:41:47,280 --> 00:41:47,840
You...

1101
00:41:48,230 --> 00:41:49,110
No one's eavesdropping.

1102
00:41:49,360 --> 00:41:50,190
We just came downstairs

1103
00:41:50,230 --> 00:41:51,630
and saw you on the phone.

1104
00:41:52,070 --> 00:41:53,440
You just said you trust

1105
00:41:53,440 --> 00:41:54,880
Wanzhi the most.

1106
00:41:54,960 --> 00:41:56,230
So who were you consulting?

1107
00:41:57,190 --> 00:41:58,070
My...

1108
00:41:58,670 --> 00:41:59,510
a...

1109
00:41:59,710 --> 00:42:00,440
um...

1110
00:42:01,150 --> 00:42:01,840
a friend.

1111
00:42:02,030 --> 00:42:02,920
Boyfriend?

1112
00:42:03,190 --> 00:42:03,670
Zhao Jun,

1113
00:42:03,710 --> 00:42:04,920
are you dating someone?

1114
00:42:05,110 --> 00:42:05,920
Is he reliable?

1115
00:42:06,230 --> 00:42:06,960
Bring him home

1116
00:42:07,000 --> 00:42:08,030
so Wanzhi can check him out.

1117
00:42:08,320 --> 00:42:08,920
No,

1118
00:42:09,070 --> 00:42:10,190
it's a friend.

1119
00:42:10,630 --> 00:42:11,710
He's in Beijing now.

1120
00:42:12,110 --> 00:42:13,590
He's not my boyfriend.

1121
00:42:13,800 --> 00:42:14,840
He's a good student,

1122
00:42:14,960 --> 00:42:15,880
so I trust him quite a bit.

1123
00:42:16,190 --> 00:42:16,710
Of course,

1124
00:42:16,880 --> 00:42:18,280
I trust Auntie Wanzhi the most.

1125
00:42:19,710 --> 00:42:20,110
Juan.

1126
00:42:20,320 --> 00:42:21,190
Stop joking.

1127
00:42:21,670 --> 00:42:22,920
Have you decided on a name yet?

1128
00:42:23,280 --> 00:42:23,920
Yes,

1129
00:42:24,320 --> 00:42:25,230
it's Shenxian Peak.

1130
00:42:26,320 --> 00:42:27,480
Does your friend

1131
00:42:27,510 --> 00:42:28,510
agree with it too?

1132
00:42:30,030 --> 00:42:30,960
Auntie Wanzhi.

1133
00:42:40,760 --> 00:42:42,320
Put that toilet paper over there.

1134
00:42:42,550 --> 00:42:43,360
- Okay!
- Okay!

1135
00:42:45,070 --> 00:42:46,000
Mr. Gao,

1136
00:42:46,590 --> 00:42:47,960
you sent two flower baskets.

1137
00:42:48,280 --> 00:42:49,280
Thanks.

1138
00:42:49,840 --> 00:42:50,920
Zhao Jun was my student

1139
00:42:51,000 --> 00:42:51,880
and my class monitor.

1140
00:42:51,880 --> 00:42:52,710
Of course I had to come

1141
00:42:52,710 --> 00:42:53,880
on her first business venture.
